Designed to mimic the exoskeleton of its creators, the [[Verpine/Legends|Verpine]], '''Verpine Bond Gauntlets''' were formed from tensor mesh materials which stiffened the forearm of the user. They functioned similarly to the [[stabilizer gauntlets]], allowing the user to safely handle volatile objects.

